high_descs: Turn around and go to the bedroom to your left, and go to the sidetable right to the bed.
Pick up the potato from the side table.
Turn around and walk straight ahead, head to the counter and to the microwave to your right.
Put the potato into the microwave.
Go to the right side of the countertop
Pick up the other potato next to the yellow towel.
Go back to the microwave.
Put the potato into the microwave again.
Turn around. Move on. At the end of the wall, turn right. Enter the room. Turn right. Turn left. Approach the sidetable.
Grab the potato.
Turn around. Leave the room. Turn left, go forward and then turn right. Keep going forward to the microwave. Turn right.
Open the microwave door. Place the potato on the left side of the microwave. Close the door.
Turn right, move a little and turn left.
Grab the potato.
Turn around. Turn right. Move forward and turn right to the microwave.
Open the microwave. Place the potato behind the other potato. Close the microwave door.
anns.task_desc: Find two potatoes and place Potato inside the Microwave.

high_descs: Head rotate and turn left to the side table.
Pick the potato from the side table.
Turn left and turn right to the microwave.
Put the potato from the microwave.
Pick it out of the microwave from the countertop.
Turn left and pick the potato from the countertop.
Turn right to the microwave.
Put the potato from the microwave.
anns.task_desc: To put the potato from the microwave.
